 edson l outwin for  under willits and outwins the company expanded into the catheter business introducing the foley catheter in  and the america woven catheter in  in  bards annual sales topped  million for the first time and the company moved its headquarters from new york city to summit new jersey in  a bard scientist dr debakey developed the first arterial prosthesiscitation needed three years later the company began selling foley catheters that came in sterile packaging for the first time ever bard continued to innovate in the world of catheters rolling out the bipolar temporary pacing catheter in  and the first latex balloon catheter in  in  bard expanded beyond catheters and began manufacturing products related to cardiology radiology and anesthesiology bard went public in  and was listed on the new york stock exchange in  the company has introduced a variety of new health care products since that time its net sales first exceeded  billion in  around  bard acquired the company lutonix on april   it was announced that bard would be bought by becton dickinson for  billion productsedit bard specializes in the manufacturing of vascular urology oncology and surgical specialty products illegal kickback settlementedit in  bard agreed to pay  million to resolve kickback allegations filed against the company relating to submitting false claims to medicare the complaint filed in  alleges bard paid illegal kickbacks to both physicians and consumers vaginal mesh device lawsuitsedit vaginal mesh devices are threaded into the vagina to treat incontinence or to fortify pelvic muscles some women have charged that the devices are poorly designed and contain materials that are unsafe for use in humans and that some require multiple surgeries to remove in  the us food and drug administration requested that bard and other vaginalmesh makers study rates of organ damage linked to the mesh devices in  bard began negotiations to settle nearly  legal claims related to implantable vaginal meshes made by the company in august  it was announced that bard had agreed to pay more than  million to resolve at least  of the legal cases related to the devices the settlement resolves about onefifth of the outstanding suits related to the implants bard said in court filings its devices are safe and effective bard vena cava filteredit an inferior vena cava filter or more simply a blood clot filter is a device that is surgically placed in the vena cava artery to prevent blood clots from moving into the heart or lungs which can be fatal on december   nbc news released information about an investigation that they had conducted of the bard g series filters which had replaced an earlier version the recovery filter introduced in  the recovery filter was associated with  deaths and several hundred nonfatal problems and a confidential study commissioned by bard showed that the recovery filter had higher rates of relative risk for death filter fracture and movement than all of its competitors however according to the nbc report the g series filters were a modified version of the recovery filter and bard was aware that it had similar and potentially fatal flaws shortly after it was put on the market but instead of recalling the replacement filters they were kept on the market for five years according to bard and fda records at least  deaths and hundreds of problems have been linked to the g series filters referencesedit  a b c cr bard bcr annual sec income statement filing via wikinvest  a b cr bard bcr annual sec balance sheet filing via wikinvest  cr bard at yahoo finance  httpbdandbardtransactionannouncementcom  a b cr bard negotiating to settle thousands of lawsuits involving vaginalmesh implants njcom retrieved  april    anthony hallett diane hallett entrepreneur magazine encyclopedia of entrepreneurs page    charles r bard  during a trip to europe he encountered a medicine called gomenol derived from the eucalyptus tree which relieved his   george john septembe